Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得揍扁多少个蠢货\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}How many of these goons do we have to bap
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他们才会长教训\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}before they get the hint?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.03,0:00:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 他们一直不停地冒出来\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Really. They just keep coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.61,0:00:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候启动B计划了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Time to switch to plan B.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,多纳泰罗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Donatello?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.26,0:00:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就好 李奥\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Almost there, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,巴士即将出发 前往任何地方\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}This bus now leaving for anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.84,0:00:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,反正不是这里\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2} but here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,快走 我们出发\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Come on! We're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 开得真好 多尼\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Whoa! Nice driving, Don,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.16,0:01:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,对于一只没驾照的乌龟来说\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}for a turtle with no license!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.39,0:01:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你想要中看还是中用\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Hey, you want pretty, or you want effective?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我得告诉你 今天真是诡异的一天\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I gotta tell you, this has been one mondo bizarro day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,首先是地下那些金属机器人\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}First, all those metal robot things underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.79,0:01:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,还有那些忍者是怎么回事\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}And what's with all those ninjas?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,纽约除了我们还有别的忍者?\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Ninjas in New York City? Besides us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.09,0:01:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这太不对劲了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}It's just not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,说到不对劲\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Talk about not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,快来看看这个\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看这些钱 宝贝\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Show me the money, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,喔吼\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Whoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不是谁捡到就归谁 麦奇\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}This isn't finders keepers, Mikey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.99,0:01:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们 看好这些钱 行吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Take care of this money, will you, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你看见了吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.69,0:01:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,一些开装甲车的小绿人\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Some little green men in an armored car
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,朝我们扔了一大堆钱\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}just threw a bunch of money at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:01:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,哈 菜鸟\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Rookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.68,0:02:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 你没事\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Sensei, you're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.66,0:02:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,斯普林特! 好哎!\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}- Splinter! - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我也很高兴看到你们\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Yes, well, I'm glad to see you, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子们\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}my sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.96,0:02:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,斯普林特老师\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Master Splinter,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,今天发生了太多事\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}so much has happened today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 好的\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,稍后有的是时间告诉我\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}There will be time to tell me all about it later
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,李奥纳多\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Leonardo,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.27,0:02:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但首先\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}but first,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我想先带你们回家\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I wish to take you all home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,家?\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有家了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}We got no home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那些机器人把我们的家毁了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Those robots trashed our pad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.54,0:02:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,还记得吗 老师\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Remember, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我已经找到了方法\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I think I have found a solution
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,解决我们的住房问题\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}to our current housing problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来 孩子们\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Follow me, my sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,卡哇邦....\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Cowabun--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这不好笑 拉夫\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Not funny, Raph!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:02:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 当然好笑\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Oh, yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,超赞的滑行\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Wicked slide!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,无意冒犯 斯普林特老师\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}No offense, Master Splinter,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但这地方看起来不怎么样\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}but this place doesn't seem so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,用心去看 米开朗基罗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Look with your heart, Michelangelo,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是用你的眼睛\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}and not your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 好吧\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Um, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,往这边走\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}And walk this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,哇\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这简直太棒了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}This is beyond awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以把这里改造一下\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I could really tune this space up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这间屋子 归我了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}This room here, mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你站的那里 也是我的\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}And where you're standing, also mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,听着孩子们 改变是好事\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You see, my sons, change is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们完全赞同 斯普林特老师\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}We couldn't agree more, Master Splinter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这次换你们几个来打扫吧\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}So let's see you boys clean up for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这房间太脏了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}This chamber is filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,唉 老兄\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Aw, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 我...我...\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Sir? I--I--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我的手下们\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}my men,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们...我们把运钞的装甲车弄丢了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}we--we lost the armored car with the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们是被袭击了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}But we were attacked
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,被某种空手道青蛙生物之类的袭击\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}by some sort of karate frog creatures or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他们打了我们一个措手不及\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}They took us by surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是我的错\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}It wasn't my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,够了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证 先生 我不会再让你失望了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I promise, sir, I won't fail you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会再让我失望了 永远\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You won't fail me again, ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不 先生 求你了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}No, sir! Please!
